text: Imaclava is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Drilliidae. ==Species== Species within the genus Imaclava include: * Imaclava asaedai (Hertlein & Strong, 1951) * Imaclava hotei (Otuka, 1949) * Imaclava ima Bartsch, 1944 * Imaclava pembertoni (H.N. Lowe, 1935) * Imaclava pilsbryi Bartsch, 1950 * Imaclava unimaculata (Sowerby I, 1834) ;Species brought into synonymy: * Imaclava hosoi Okutani, 1964: synonym of Crassispira hosoi (Okutani, 1964) ==References== ==External links== Category:Gastropod genera
title: Imaclava
